Layer 1: sphereql-core (Pure Spherical Math)
Types

SphericalPoint { r, theta, phi } -- (r >= 0, theta in [0, 2PI), phi in [0, PI])
CartesianPoint { x, y, z }
GeoPoint { lat, lon, alt }
Regions: Cone, Cap, Shell, Band, Wedge, Region (compound via Intersection/Union)

Functions

Conversions: spherical <-> cartesian <-> geo
Distance: angular_distance (Vincenty formula, NOT spherical law of cosines -- numerically stable), great_circle_distance, chord_distance, euclidean_distance
Containment: Contains trait implemented for all region types
Interpolation: slerp, nlerp, full_slerp (interpolates r + direction)

